{"id":60,"title":"问：什么是goroutine？它与操作系统线程相比有什么特点？","slug":"问：什么是goroutine？它与操作系统线程相比有什么特点？-1766595052","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：goroutine是Go语言中一种轻量级的“用户级线程”，由Go运行时调度管理。相对于OS线程，goroutine创建和切换的成本更低，每个goroutine初始栈空间很小（可按需动态扩展），因此在Go程序中可以同时启动成千上万个goroutine而不会像线程那样耗尽资源。Go运行时采用GMP调度模型**（G=goroutine，M=内核线程，P=调度器）实现对goroutine的**M:N调度**，多个goroutine可以复用少量操作系统线程来实现高并发。当一个goroutine阻塞（例如IO操作）时，Go调度器会智能地让其它goroutine继续在同一线程上运行。总之，goroutine提供了更廉价的并发抽象，使得**大规模并发**在Go中变得易于使用。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:52.96473+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:52.96473+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-80ac-99a2-ca67027951de","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":60,"blog_post_id":60,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.609593+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.609593+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:52.96473+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:52.96473+08:00"}